  "raw_text": "together one method is information. Even the primordial catastrophe - the bomb blast is depicted - after which world is not real (but the characters do not understand their state) This is why 3-74 always turns out to resemble \"Ubik.\" When the cosmos ruptured, reality died. If Pythagoras is right, only cosmos is real because only cosmos has the essential structure (which can be regarded as the intelligable). (I.e. Christ n The rational But, it would seem is immanent in the reality which he is bringing into existence by his integrating or structuring; it is indeed a cosmic body blended into the atelos or disintegrating former cosmos which is no longer a cosmos at This is precisely \"Falsework\" irreal. all + hence situation \"Ubik\" where the in is 241 not only disorder but irreal, +, penetrating it, is Ubik which is not the same as it but none‐ theless is everywhere. The relationship between The world + Ubik is precisely that of the debris of the former cosmos to the cosmic Christ - + the nature of the world in \"Ubik\" is that of the world here, + Ubik's that of the cosmic Christ or Logos. So in \"Ubik\" I have pictured our actual condition. Thus we are essentially in the situation of half-lifers, experiencing a counterfeit reality composed of boosted memory or former thought formations of our own minds; if it should happen that we recognize an event as an exteriorization of a former thought content of our own mind we - that mind - is at once converted, as Eckehart taught, into - not Jesus - but the Father the creator himself, author of world who has literally thought it into existence + now must undergo c endure) it immediately the role between self + world reverses instead of world impinging as macrocosm on self as microcoum, the self - as Father - is holder of all creative power + melts the causal train events of world which has now assumed the aspect of mere thought-projection, like a hologram, under the father's control Ubik is the projected present total mind I The Father underlying + governing world. it is mirror to the center, the Father who has recovered his lost identity + brought his remory forward in time by going backward in time to the sacred mythic beginnings 247 world is mind + self is author. The lag vanishes; former thought projections rush past until inner + outer time are synchronized. \"Karma\" the power of prior thought formations, is broken (\"astral or planetary determinism\"). The selfprogramming, in which the mind is the vior o victim of its own conceptions is burned or used up in a furious rush forward, as if the programming tape speeds up faster + faster until it runs out - at which point the pure mind of the person com‐ prises world. The Father has been born in the soul: the soul is the creator of the Father + hence the Godhead (grund) itself. beyond this lies only a vast desert, a void of spacial infinity without time, where Godhead as non-being exists the universe has been abolished. This is Nirvana: nothingness. First world was exteriorization of the mind's own prior con‐ epts, fears hopes, beliefs + thoughts. Then, upon these being recognized for what they are or rather were) world is replaced by the mind itself, but mind of the Father now born in the soul, then the void of the God read replaces that. The mind's ability to tart the process by recognizing its world its own prior thought contents comes thrag the Holy Spirit namnesis + this is induced by on who enlightens the mind which otherwise ould remain in perpetual forgetfuln 3 sequence: 1) World as Karma - i.e. prior thought forma tions completely controlling the mind + pinging on the person: a counterfeit reality 2) Anamnesis, brought on by the Holy the person remembers his true identity. Spirit. 3) Christ is born in the mind + takes control. karma (the power of the prior thought forma ons of the mind) is broken. Christ has defeated these ossified thoughts + started up real time + real world (for the person not its contents 4) World as mind of the person (Valis) who is now no longer the son but the creator, the Father; hence world is as under mind's power as mind formerly was under world's the positions of the two have reversed, absolutely. 5) The Godhead: the desert or void of non‐ being + bliss. The 3 persons of the trinity are gone. Nothing remains, world is abolished. time does not exist, only space. 6) World returns, freed of the ossified power + presence of prior thought formations the Bardo Thodol trip is over; the person has been born. Fate is overcome. 7) The second comforter is with him unto the end, in syzygy with him as his divine sister. This means that the birth was successful a binary brain mind now exists able to generate the infinite logic of the dialectic which underlies reality; this the role of Father is retained in the Logos sense: as meta‐ the images, concepts word ught re 74 i s a Garden world or magic Kingdom, from which we originally fell t The person is not alone but has been assimilated by the divine in a relationship of parity. God has become man & as a result man has become God. the process is complete: the new Adam is here & the old Adam, in bondage to his own prior thought formations, has died. thus the past has yielded to the future. Time is now free to flow from disorder to order, from the irrational to the rational. The present mind has vanquished its antecedent [seel], as microcosm & as macrocosm, [mirroring] each other. The result of this process is a net yield of added energy to the total system, which is the true goal, ie that the universe be perpetual & not [run] down. This is what is meant by repair of the original rupture or fall or crisis in the Godhead. The key term, 1 is: salvation. [?] [denoting] all this Note: the progression is from 1) [former] thought contents of mind as world to 2) Mind itself as world to 3) disappearance of world entirely. There is also a progression backward from Holy Spirit to Son to Father to Godhead, & then to world [regained], 2 & [?] with the Holy Spirit forever, so a permanent result accrues. There is also a progression from conterfeit world to real world to supernatural world to nonbeing & then back to real, but never to counterfeit. When world disappears the creator disappears because he is involved in his [own?] semi-illusory creation. Here's a major point I never met up until now; would recognizing an event as a prior thought form cause anamnesis? Or would anamnesis occur & as a result you would recognize an event as a prior thought form because now you didnt have the memory block? I think the former. The pharmacy girl came to the *door* & I underwent the shock of recognition - & for a split second the memory block (amnesia) lifted. It had happened a long time ago (Before). Hence I saw the world as ancient. This is why the 2 views (perceptions) of it were syntonic. This, all this, had happened before, a long time ago; so of course it - the landscapes - looked ancient; it was actually ancient - [served] up again (as [Lem] discusses: [World] based largely on memories. All this which I saw was events 2000 years (or so) in the past, actually. Fed to me again much later, consciously forgotten. It had leaked through in [] form into [\"MITHC\"] \"facts of\" etc. this means: Acts: USA 1974: : USA 1974: the [true present?]. Then we are actually not living in 1974 [so] [but] much later (which explains why I sensed \"it\" or \"them\" as coming from the future, the 3-eyed people as our remote descendents. They are on the other side of the glass, alive, in the \"moratorium.\" We are in \"cold pac.\" Now, this is something I absolutely never guessed as an [explanation]. It would explain the \"one way [uncanny intrusions.\"] 1939:1992: : 1974: x. Just it was not really 1939 for the inertials in \"UBIK\" but 1992, it is not really 1974 for [] (or us, whichever). Hence my sense of time dysfunction, in 1974. This would explain the AI voice, this would explain Valis operating \"behind\" or \"in\" or \"inside\" or \"beyond\" reality; it is the computer (3?) running the program = UBIK Would explain the plasmate info controlling us. Valis is the true reality; the phenomenal world is our prior memories or prior events fed back to us: phylogenic memories. So of course Valis can meet causal [trains]. Can program us of course causality is really pretextual, & really only signals that disinhinit inner progrmming. & of course \"God\" is deus absconditus. Now: 1) I remembered 2-3-74, esp. the Xerox Missive. This is how I knew it was coming & exactly which day. 2) Who/what pre-empted me & took motor control? Why, Valis (whatever that is) - which is outside, [like] Runciter not in \"cold-pac.\" a computer-like entity? 3) I would be willing to bet that I requested a second go-around (esp. vis-a-vis the Xerox Missive). 4) They can modulate any & all events (signals) which impinge on us to obtain the desired results (responses) from us. 5) \"UBIK\" is basically the [correct] paradigm. 6) The AI voice. Like Reunciter's to Ella. Someone (\"Diana\") is patched into me from the other side (called by her \"the [Ubik realm??]\"). 7) Valis. The memories from my \"half-life\" brain, as fed to world-generator were modulated by an intelligent entity or construct with power to control reality resulting from the memory input. [Memory fed in as in-put] [2 Valis as world generator using input as source] [3 Me or us] [4 Prior thought formations] Total feedback loop. the key clue was my viewing USA 1974 as the distant past which I suddenly remembered. My Amnesia (Memory Block) gone. I was there (USA 1974) centuries ago. Then the rest - the AI voice, Valis, the time dysfunction, the pages of Info!! the 3-eyed people, etc., all fit into place. Pretextual cause, programming & disinhibition, the pre-emtion of me by \"Thomas\" - all the cosmological etc concepts suddenly in my head - the vast [other] mind. The plasmate info fed subliminally to us, our occluded perceptions, & the remarkable resemblance, always, to \"UBIK.\" & - my 27 years of saying that reality is simulated - now \"joint\" - the soft drink stand - it makes sense. Back to \"EYE.\" 3-74 verifies the \"reality is simulated\" realization of decades. Esp. \"UBIK\" if not \"Maze.\" 27 3-74 the two years of & halves. reality is Valis problem & verification. But I've misssed the crucial simulated clue; Viz: that Valis is in control of our whole reality because our memories pass through it to get to us, so in my opinion this is a technologically contrived - highly sophisticated - situation. If the \"Onion Layers\" model of time put forth in \"UBIK\" is correct our world would [ebb] back naturally, disclosing prior forms within as far as we were [concerned] - as Claudia points out [re] \"UBIK,\" but this is an [illusion]; the real world has not regressed. So I did time-[bind] so fast in 3-74 that I must have stabilized for a moment against the regressing, which made Valis visible to me for just a moment: Valis is the real nature of our reality: a constant signalling system. I must have been leaving cold pac faster & faster, synchronizing with the control system (Valis) which must move faster than the system it controls. This idea that we're in a simulated reality (which Valis generates & controls) seems less unlikely when one considers Brahmanism: Brahman",
